  <thing id="fS2ImpResi" name="Improved Resiliency" description="You gain a construct&apos;s resistance to nonlethal damage.{br}{br}{b}Prerequisite:{/b} Warforged.{br}{br}{b}Benefit:{/b} You are immune to nonlethal damage but lose the ability to benefit from regeneration or fast healing, even if you would gain those qualities through magic or the application of a template." compset="Feat" summary="You can no benefit from regeneration or fast healing." uniqueness="useronce">
