  <thing id="fS2SecSlam" name="Second Slam" description="You have learned to use your form to the utmost and can make two slam attacks.{br}{br}{b}Prerequisites:{/b} Warforged, base attack bonus +6.{br}{br}{b}Benefit:{/b} You can deliver a second slam in any round in which you make a full attack that includes a slam attack. The second slam uses your highest attack bonus with a - 5 penalty, and deals your normal slam attack damage." compset="Feat" summary="Don&apos;t crit to make 2nd attack. If successfull make a Fort save or be Paralyzed." uniqueness="useronce">
